text: Sandugo is a 2019 Philippine drama television series starring Ejay Falcon, and Aljur Abrenica. The series aired on ABS-CBN's Kapamilya Gold afternoon block and worldwide via The Filipino Channel from September 30, 2019 to March 20, 2020, replacing Precious Hearts Romances Presents: Los Bastardos. ==Series overview== ==Episodes== ===Season 1=== ==References== Category:Lists of Philippine drama television series episodes
